        "On the 21st August 2018, my sister is entering into conjugal relation and being the most adored child, my parents want this event to be blissful. On the other hand, this event demands my presence, inorder to follow certain traditional rituals that is compelling me to request this leave starting the 15th until 29th August 2018.",
